around here. The anime is finally complete.

258
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:06,230
I'm starting to get nervous.

259
00:15:06,230 --> 00:15:08,310
Me, too, Milady.

260
00:15:08,310 --> 00:15:10,540
Excited. Can't wait.

261
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:12,510
I can't wait to see it.

262
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:15,220
I plan on crying three times during this movie.

263
