274
00:15:56,740 --> 00:16:00,860
A tie-in. I thought about putting some commercials in there, too.

275
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,110
Here comes the feature show.

276
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:04,010
Britney always looks at her senpai from a distance.

277
00:17:04,010 --> 00:17:06,560
What? What is this picture?

278
00:17:09,730 --> 00:17:11,340
