279
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:15,540
I made lunch. Would you like to eat with me?

280
00:17:16,890 --> 00:17:19,610
Ah, that sounds good. Let us.

281
00:17:19,610 --> 00:17:21,590
What? I'm in the show.

282
00:17:21,590 --> 00:17:23,540
Yes, what is this?

283
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:25,940
Britney loves her senpai so much.

284
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:28,570
But she can never bring herself to say that.

285
00:17:28,570 --> 00:17:31,070
Because she's a magical girl!? That isn't the reason.

286
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:33,980
Because the senpai... senpai has!

287
00:17:34,650 --> 00:17:37,540
He already has a wife and a child.

288
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:41,470
I-It really is a surprising development.

289
00:17:41,470 --> 00:17:43,900
I can't really accept the character setting.

290
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:47,670
The more you stir-

291
00:17:47,670 --> 00:17:50,450
But due to an evil witch's power-

292
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,180
Neru Neru Ne~

293
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:56,520
Senpai was turned into a star.

294
00:17:59,870 --> 00:18:02,130
Because of that, the wife fell sick,

295
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:04,410
and the child became a punk.

296
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:10,540
When you're about to lose in
a net game, just cut the network off!

297
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:14,170
The tension is starting to build.

298
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:18,010
Britney decides to return senpai back to human form.

299
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:23,440
But even if she succeeds, senpai will return to his wife's side.

300
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:25,810
There is no chance of him getting together with Britney.

301
00:18:27,370 --> 00:18:32,080
However, if she goes on a journey, she will be able to be with senpai,

302
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,930
