303
00:18:33,930 --> 00:18:35,560
What will you do, Britney?

304
00:18:35,560 --> 00:18:38,000
The decision Britney made is:

305
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:43,430
Life of a Kitty.

306
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:45,400
Run. Run. Run. Run.

307
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:47,730
Run. Run. Run. Run.

