313
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:11,140
How was it? Did you understand my manga a little-

314
00:19:11,140 --> 00:19:13,290
What's wrong?

315
00:19:25,260 --> 00:19:26,170
Come in.

316
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,890
Oh, Maria-san.

317
00:19:28,890 --> 00:19:30,460
Hayate-kun.

318
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:32,670
You're here, as well.

319
00:19:32,670 --> 00:19:36,040
Does that mean you're here for the same reason as me?

320
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:39,660
Yes. I wanted to read Milady's manga one more time.

321
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:43,900
Since she did put a lot of effort into drawing it.

322
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:46,500
Yes. We should understand it more.

323
00:19:47,410 --> 00:19:51,600
Also, I'm eager to find out what happens to Britney-chan and the senpai.

324
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:54,780
I am, too, a little.

325
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:56,040
But, Hataye-kun.

326
00:19:57,540 --> 00:19:58,480
Yes?

327
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:02,060
