345
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,420
You don't like it?

346
00:21:05,420 --> 00:21:06,420
In that case-

347
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:11,220
You'd better make your choice.

348
00:21:12,180 --> 00:21:15,080
